=\"20\" /> No more exporting to excel to manipulate complex data.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/b/5b8eb55b23c5111b286e11da3ef7089a251c223d.png\" title=\"1\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/5/b/5b8eb55b23c5111b286e11da3ef7089a251c223d_2_517x258.png\" alt=\"1\" width=\"517\" height=\"258\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">1</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×960 116 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
